# iOS CoreML Reference Bundle

Base model: `{{BASE_MODEL}}`

## Prerequisites
- macOS 14+
- Xcode 15+
- Swift 5.9+
- Optional: `xcodegen` (auto-generates `.xcodeproj` from `ios/project.yml`)

## Model Placement
1. Copy your exported model into `ios/ModelAssets/model.mlmodelc/`.
2. Keep tokenizer/config metadata beside the model when available.
3. Optional fallback binary path: `ios/ModelAssets/model.bin`.

## Run Instructions
1. Run: `bash scripts/run_ios_app.sh`
2. Open the generated `ios/SLMReference.xcodeproj` in Xcode.
3. Build and run the `SLMReference` scheme on simulator/device.

## Smoke Inference
Run: `bash scripts/run_smoke.sh "Hello from iOS"`
